OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver who reached
OL,4,C80mph in 30 zone jailed
OL,6,FVideo of the police pursuit shows Paul
OL,7,FRudkin driving dangerously before
OL,8,Fcrashing - Credit: Sussex Police
OL,10,FA driver who was high on cocaine
OL,11,Fwhilst he sped at 80mph in a 30 zone
OL,12,Fin West Sussex has been jailed.
OL,14,FPaul Rudkin, 42, failed to stop for
OL,15,Fpolice in Keymer Road, Burgess Hill,
OL,16,Fand attempted dangerous overtaking of
OL,17,Fother vehicles.
OL,19,FRudkin was driving a blue Mini Cooper
OL,20,Fwhen he hit a puddle and lost control.
OL,21,FHe was then arrested by police.
