OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver who reached
OL,4,C80mph in 30 zone jailed
OL,6,FIt was found that he was once again
OL,7,Fmore than ten times the legal limit
OL,8,Ffor cocaine in his system.
OL,10,FAt Crawley Magistrates' Court on April
OL,11,F10 he admitted two counts of drug
OL,12,Fdriving, following an earlier hearing
OL,13,Fat Lewes Crown Court on January 8
OL,14,Fwhere Rudkin was sentenced to ten
OL,15,Fmonths in prison.
