OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver who reached
OL,4,C80mph in 30 zone jailed
OL,6,FFollowing the first sentencing in
OL,7,FJanuary, Rudkin admitted failing to
OL,8,Fstop, driving without insurance, and
OL,9,Fdangerous driving, and has been
OL,10,Fdisqualified from driving for three
OL,11,Fyears and four months.
OL,13,FThen on April 10 he admitted two
OL,14,Fcharges relating to drug driving. He
OL,15,Fwas given a further three year
OL,16,Fdisqualification and ordered to pay a
OL,17,F#32 surcharge and #80 fine.
