OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver who reached
OL,4,C80mph in 30 zone jailed
OL,6,FThe court was told how the incident
OL,7,Fhappened at 11.20am on December 10
OL,8,Flast year, during Sussex Police's
OL,9,Fannual campaign to tackle drink and
OL,10,Fdrug drivers during the festive period.
OL,12,FFootage showed Rudkin, formerly a
OL,13,Flandscape gardener of Bentswood Road,
OL,14,FHaywards Heath, drive away from
OL,15,Fofficers.
OL,17,FHe narrowly avoided head-on collisions
OL,18,Fand completed high risk overtaking on
OL,19,Fblind bends.
