OL,3,CCocaine-fuelled driver who reached
OL,4,C80mph in 30 zone jailed
OL,6,FThe pursuit finished after he lost
OL,7,Fcontrol and crashed into a hedge.
OL,9,FHis blood test showed he had 110
OL,10,Fmicrograms (uhg) of cocaine per litre
OL,11,Fof blood. The legal limit is 10uhg of
OL,12,Fcocaine per litre of blood.
OL,14,FHe also tested positive for more than
OL,15,F800uhg of a cocaine breakdown chemical
OL,16,Fcalled Benzoylecgonine, the legal
OL,17,Flimit for this chemical is 50uhg per
OL,18,Flitre of blood.
