OL,6,FAt an earlier hearing at Crawley
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on December 11 last
OL,8,Fyear he admitted drug driving relating
OL,9,Fto a separate offence on July 12 last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FRudkin was found slumped over the
OL,13,Fwheel of his vehicle in Jobs Lane,
OL,14,FHickstead. He gave a positive DrugWipe
OL,15,Ftest for cocaine.
OL,17,FOn that occasion a sample of his blood
OL,18,Fshowed he had 109 microgrammes (ug) of
OL,19,Fcocaine per litre of blood in his
OL,20,Fsystem. The legal limit is 10ug of
OL,21,Fcocaine per litre of blood.
