OL,6,FInvestigating officer PC Max Setra
OL,7,Ffrom the Roads Policing Unit said:
OL,8,F"Rudkin's driving put himself, his
OL,9,Fpassengers and other road users at
OL,10,Frisk.
OL,12,F"He was highly fortunate not to cause
OL,13,Fa head-on collision as he reached high
OL,14,Fspeeds in Burgess Hill.
OL,16,F"We are pleased with the outcome of
OL,17,Fthe case. It demonstrates our
OL,18,Fdetermination to catch offenders and
OL,19,Ftake dangerous drivers off our roads."
