OL,6,FOfficers across Sussex Police are
OL,7,Fcurrently conducting road safety
OL,8,Fpatrols as part of the force's "fatal
OL,9,Ffive" campaign this April.
OL,11,FDrink and drug driving is one of the
OL,12,Fmain causes in people being killed or
OL,13,Fseriously injured on our roads.
OL,15,FThe other factors are driving at
OL,16,Fexcess speed, not wearing a seat belt,
OL,17,Fbeing distracted while driving such as
OL,18,Fby using a mobile phone, and careless
OL,19,For anti-social driving.
